<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53001636/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription "The purpose of the advanced seminars is to present current research topics providing presentations and lectures from invited professors or experts in the area of interest. These seminars allow students to improve their knowledge in areas that are not covered with other subjects which has a much more fundamental content. Therefore, the planning and the agenda of each seminar depend on each lecture and invited professor."@es .

